Metadata.Title: Guard For Hire: Sleeping With A Drug Lord
Metadata.Description: Since inflation has gone up recently, the ICA has been giving their agents less pay because of the increased prices. Many agents, including the one and only 47, doesn't like this move, and so, quite a few of those people who are upset with the situation, have tried to find side-jobs. A few of them have joined the military, one even got a job at McDonald's, But 47 is different. 47 has decided that he wants to become...A bodyguard for the famous drug cartel leader Rico Delgado!*whispering* And let's just say, his applications have returned with no avail.47 believes it's because Delgado has too many guards already stationed in his mansion. His handler Diana believes it's because no dope peddler wants a Caucasian man in his mid-50s working for them. Regardless, 47 has decided to to eliminate a few of the current incumbents, so that he may have a shot at getting the job. Good luck.
